函数原型
====

```python
Series.plot(kind='line', ax=None, figsize=None, use_index=True, title=None, grid=None,   
legend=False, style=None, logx=False, logy=False, loglog=False, xticks=None, yticks=None,   
xlim=None, ylim=None, rot=None, fontsize=None, colormap=None, table=False, yerr=None,  
xerr=None, label=None, secondary_y=False, **kwds)
```

注：要使用 plot 函数需要使用 matplotlib 和 pylab 环境。`%matplotlib inline`

参数
==
<table border="2">
    <tbody><tr>
        <th>参数</th>
        <th>类型</th>
        <th>说明</th>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td>kind</td>
        <td>str</td>
        <td>
            <ul>
                <li>‘line’: 默认值。线性图。例：tz_counts[:20].plot(kind=’line’, rot=0)</li>
                <li>‘bar’：垂直条形图。例：tz_counts[:20].plot(kind=’bar’, rot=0)</li>
                <li>‘barh’：水平条形图。例：tz_counts[:20].plot(kind=’barh’, rot=0)</li>
                <li>‘hist’：柱状图。例：tz_counts[:20].plot(kind=’hist’, rot=0)</li>
                <li>‘box’：box plot。例：tz_counts[:20].plot(kind=’box’, rot=0)</li>
                <li>‘kde’：核密度估计 Kernel Density Estimation(KDE)</li>
                <li>‘density’：和’kde’相同</li>
                <li>‘area’：面积图。例：tz_counts[:20].plot(kind=’area’, rot=0)</li>
                <li>‘pie’：饼图。例：tz_counts[:20].plot(kind=’pie’, rot=0)</li>
                </ul>
    </td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
    <td>ax </td>
    <td>matplotlib axes object。matplotlib 轴对象</td>
    <td>如果未传参，使用 gca()</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
    <td>figsize </td>
    <td>元组 tuple (width, height)</td>
    <td>图片尺寸。参数类型为一个元组。单位为英寸</td>
    </tr>   
    <tr>
    <td>use_index </td>
    <td>布尔值。默认值为 True</td>
    <td>是否使用 Series 的 index 作为 x 轴标识。</td>
    </tr>       
    <tr>
    <td>title </td>
    <td>string or list</td>
    <td>图标的标题。如果这个参数北传递进来，这个标题将显示在图片的顶部。如果一个 list 被作为参数传递进来并且 If a list is passed and subplots 为 True, 打印列表中的对象到相应的 subplot.</td>
    </tr>   
    <tr>
    <td>grid </td>
    <td>boolean, default None (matlab style default)</td>
    <td>是否显示网格。</td>
    </tr>   
    <tr>
    <td>legend </td>
    <td>False/True/’reverse’</td>
    <td>是否在图上显示坐标轴说明</td>
    </tr>       
    <tr>
    <td>style </td>
    <td>list or dict</td>
    <td>matplotlib line style per column</td>
    </tr>       
    <tr>
    <td>logx </td>
    <td>boolean, 默认值为 False</td>
    <td>Use log scaling on x axis</td>
    </tr>       
    <tr>
    <td>logy </td>
    <td>boolean, 默认值为 False</td>
    <td>Use log scaling on y axis</td>
    </tr>   
    <tr>
    <td>loglog </td>
    <td>boolean, 默认值为 False</td>
    <td>Use log scaling on both x and y axes</td>
    </tr>   
    <tr>
    <td>xticks </td>
    <td>sequence</td>
    <td>Values to use for the xticks</td>
    </tr>   
    <tr>
    <td>yticks </td>
    <td>sequence</td>
    <td>Values to use for the yticks</td>
    </tr>       
    <tr>
    <td>xlim </td>
    <td>2-tuple/list</td>
    <td rowspan="3">Rotation for ticks (xticks for vertical, yticks for horizontal plots)</td>
    </tr>       
    <tr>
    <td>ylim </td>
    <td>2-tuple/list</td>
    </tr>       
    <tr>
    <td>rot </td>
    <td> int, default None</td>
    </tr>       
    <tr>
    <td>fontsize</td>
    <td>int, default None</td>
    <td>xticks 和 yticks 的字体大小</td>
    </tr>       
    <tr>
    <td>colormap </td>
    <td>str or matplotlib colormap object, default None</td>
    <td>Colormap to select colors from. If string, load colormap with that name from matplotlib.</td>
    </tr>   
    <tr>
    <td>colorbar </td>
    <td>boolean, optional</td>
    <td>If True, plot colorbar (only relevant for ‘scatter’ and ‘hexbin’ plots)</td>
    </tr>   
    <tr>
    <td>position </td>
    <td>float</td>
    <td>定义条形图条形形状的相对位置。取值范围是 0~1。0 代表 left/bottom-end，1 代表 right/top-end，默认值是 0.5(中间)</td>
    </tr>       
<tr>
<td>table</td> <td>boolean, Series or DataFrame, default False</td>
<td>
    If True, draw a table using the data in the DataFrame and the data will be transposed to meet matplotlib’s default layout. If a Series or DataFrame is passed, use passed data to draw a table.</td>
    </tr>
<tr>
<td>yerr </td><td>DataFrame, Series, array-like, dict and str</td>
<td>
    See Plotting with Error Bars for detail.</td>
    </tr>
<tr>
<td>xerr </td> <td></td><td>same types as yerr.</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>label</td><td></td><td> label argument to provide to plot</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>secondary_y </td><td>boolean or sequence of ints, default False</td>
<td>
    If True then y-axis will be on the right</td>
    </tr>
<tr>
<td>mark_right</td><td>boolean, default True</td>
<td>
    When using a secondary_y axis, automatically mark the column labels with “(right)” in the legend</td>
    </tr>
<tr>
<td>kwds</td><td>keywords</td>
<td>
    Options to pass to matplotlib plotting method</td>
</tr>                                               
</tbody></table>

返回值
===

axes : matplotlib.AxesSubplot or np.array of them

注意
==

如果 kind = ‘bar’ or ‘barh’, 可以通过 position 关键字定义条形图的相对布局。 取值范围是 0~1。0 代表：left/bottom-end；1 代表：right/top-end。缺省是 0.5 (center)。
